posts.name: Duffy’s Sports Grill
posts.note: Duffy’s Sports Grill is a chain tavern catering to sports fans with a pubby American menu, all-day happy hour, and many TVs. Order the rice bowl with chicken or beef. NOTE: They have multiple locations.

posts.name: Gaspers Patio Bar and Grill
posts.note: Gaspers Patio Bar and Grill is a long-standing family-owned bar for pub grub, beer, and live music in a festive indoor/outdoor setting. You have to get the Cuban sandwich.

posts.name: Jupiter Donuts
posts.note: Jupiter Donuts start with the freshest ingredients and handcraft each and every donut. They have been committed to baking fresh donuts, bagels sandwiches, and pastries. NOTE: They have multiple locations.

posts.name: Miller’s Alehouse
posts.note: Miller’s Alehouse is a casual sports-pub chain with basics from bar snacks to steaks & a large selection of tap beers. Order their 35 shrimp Alfredo or two lobster tails for $19.95. Or the 3/4 lb special Prime Rib on Thursday. For dessert get the Captain Jack’s which is ice cream, cake, etc. NOTE: They have multiple locations.

posts.name: Satchel's Pizza
posts.note: Satchel's Pizza is a quirky cash-only institution is featuring thin-crust pies, salads, and calzones, plus outdoor seating. You need to watch Less Films video series on Satchel's Pizza.
